{"tid":1093918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"途人憂危險  兩男中環海濱放無人機被捕","createTime":"2019-04-06T02:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T06:54:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5397c6d779b81c4194ce556cabb7606813710540","tid":1093918,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190406/_2019040608584511805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190406%2F_2019040608584511805.jpg&h=d11aed9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方於昨晚約9時接報，指有人於中環海濱活動空間一帶施放無人機，擔心對附近途人造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，截查兩名分別33及40歲的本地男子，經初步調查後相信該兩名男子曾經於上址施放無人機，兩人涉嫌違反《1995年飛航(香港)令》拘捕，同時檢獲兩部懷疑與案有關的無人機。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被捕男子獲准保釋候查，須於本月上旬向警方報到。案件交由中區警區雜項調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例第448C章《1995年飛航(香港)令》列明，任何人士不得因鹵莽或疏忽操作無人機而危害他人或財產安全。警方十分重視相關案件並提醒市民，違反上述條例一經定罪，最高可被監禁兩年及判處罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1473663/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1473663%2F&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI9UqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=6c0129df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1473663%2F&h=25ebc14d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1473663/</a>"},{"pid":"cca3f11655c6a7bdcca71902489f6d2ddb337457","tid":1093918,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"係咪喺禁飛區先？<br />\n係咪因鹵莽或疏忽操作無人機而危害他人或財產安全先？<br />\n<br />\n佢兩條友下次最好哩埋先放...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbd73649e8540303df942faa9b0a2949f8ad90d","tid":1093918,"uid":42917,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:17:23.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 禁飛區都放"},{"pid":"c8acd02d96ccc1bdc3c46728a00954a0bf8f903c","tid":10939